members.name: getAlgorithm
members.comment: Returns the algorithm URI of this AlgorithmMethod.

members.name: getParameterSpec
members.comment: Returns the algorithm parameters of this AlgorithmMethod.

return: the algorithm parameters of this AlgorithmMethod. Returns null if this AlgorithmMethod does not require parameters and they are not specified.

name: javax.xml.crypto.AlgorithmMethod
comment: An abstract representation of an algorithm defined in the XML Security specifications. Subclasses represent specific types of XML security algorithms, such as a Transform.
